SENTENCE yeah .
SENTENCE um basically ,  a subduction zone is where two tectonic plates collide .
SENTENCE so if an ocean floor tectonic plate meets the edge of a continent and they push against each other ,  the heavier one sinks down and goes under the other one .
SENTENCE so the um the oceanic plate is made of denser and heavier rock ,  so it begins to sink down under the continental plate and into the mantle .
