SENTENCE slab pull happens at the subduction zone .
SENTENCE so to continue our example  as the ocean floor plate begins to sink down into the mantle ,  it would drag or pull the entire plate along with it .
SENTENCE so more and more of this plate ,  the ocean floor ,  would go down under the continent into the mantle .
